{"ja464:0.1":"Jataka ","ja464:0.2":"Dvadasakanipata ","ja464:0.3":"Culakunalavagga ","ja464:0.4":"1. Culakunalajataka ","ja464:1.1":"“Luddhanam lahucittanam, ","ja464:1.2":"akatannuna dubbhinam; ","ja464:1.3":"Nadevasatto puriso, ","ja464:1.4":"thinam saddhatumarahati. ","ja464:2.1":"Na ta pajananti katam na kiccam, ","ja464:2.2":"Na mataram pitaram bhataram va; ","ja464:2.3":"Anariya samatikkantadhamma, ","ja464:2.4":"Sasseva cittassa vasam vajanti. ","ja464:3.1":"Ciranuvutthampi piyam manapam, ","ja464:3.2":"Anukampakam panasamampi bhattum; ","ja464:3.3":"Avasu kiccesu ca nam jahanti, ","ja464:3.4":"Tasmahamitthinam na vissasami. ","ja464:4.1":"Thinanhi cittam yatha vanarassa, ","ja464:4.2":"Kannappakannam yatha rukkhachaya; ","ja464:4.3":"Calacalam hadayamitthiyanam, ","ja464:4.4":"Cakkassa nemi viya parivattati. ","ja464:5.1":"Yada ta passanti samekkhamana, ","ja464:5.2":"Adeyyarupam purisassa vittam; ","ja464:5.3":"Sanhahi vacahi nayanti menam, ","ja464:5.4":"Kambojaka jalajeneva assam. ","ja464:6.1":"Yada na passanti samekkhamana, ","ja464:6.2":"Adeyyarupam purisassa vittam; ","ja464:6.3":"Samantato nam parivajjayanti, ","ja464:6.4":"Tinno nadiparagatova kullam. ","ja464:7.1":"Silesupama sikhiriva sabbabhakkha, ","ja464:7.2":"Tikkhamaya nadiriva sighasota; ","ja464:7.3":"Sevanti heta piyamappiyanca, ","ja464:7.4":"Nava yatha orakulam paranca. ","ja464:8.1":"Na ta ekassa na dvinnam, ","ja464:8.2":"apanova pasarito; ","ja464:8.3":"Yo ta mayhanti manneyya, ","ja464:8.4":"vatam jalena badhaye. ","ja464:9.1":"Yatha nadi ca pantho ca, ","ja464:9.2":"panagaram sabha papa; ","ja464:9.3":"Evam lokitthiyo nama, ","ja464:9.4":"vela tasam na vijjati. ","ja464:10.1":"Ghatasanasama eta, ","ja464:10.2":"kanhasappasirupama; ","ja464:10.3":"Gavo bahitinasseva, ","ja464:10.4":"omasanti varam varam. ","ja464:11.1":"Ghatasanam kunjaram kanhasappam, ","ja464:11.2":"Muddhabhisittam pamada ca sabba; ","ja464:11.3":"Ete naro niccayato bhajetha, ","ja464:11.4":"Tesam have dubbidu sabbabhavo. ","ja464:12.1":"Naccantavanna na bahunam kanta, ","ja464:12.2":"Na dakkhina pamada sevitabba; ","ja464:12.3":"Na parassa bhariya na dhanassa hetu, ","ja464:12.4":"Etitthiyo panca na sevitabba”ti. ","ja464:13.1":"Culakunalajatakam pathamam. "}